{
  "stem": "13693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we knew, already, from beforehand that this what will happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because usually we used the trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the German was-- used to organize, pretty well, that they are in an orderly fashion, to take the people to Ponary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Ponary was only six or seven miles from Vilna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they took them by trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we hide them-- we hide ourself in the attics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Lithuanians finally discovered our hiding, our [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was a cry of a baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they used to go from house to house, with the metal sticks, and knock on the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one there, that you had over there the baby, and I will give you-- I wrote a story about it, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Over there, when they discovered our-- in the attic, the opening, the Lithuanian came in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the first thing what they did is they tried to get money, to be paid off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So as they collected the money, one went out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The second used to come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This one used to collect rings, and silver, and watches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A third one, till finally they came, two or three together, and they used to throw-- and they forced out everybody-- with the stick, with the scream, with all the stuff.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the beginning, they were very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this is the reason why they were volunteering for this type, especially everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But with it, I-- my-- my brother-- and I had still with my three cousins.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was a opening in the attic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So we jumped, and we crawl out, from the attic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we lay down on the roof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The German and the Lithuanian saw us, from the road, because we had to cover ourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they started to shoot in the air.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
